cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper is about modularization techniques in artificial neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the subfield of neural networks and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). However, since the paper also discusses various machine learning techniques and their applications, it could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, since modularization techniques can be applied to control systems and robotics, it could also be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
